# Summary
This documentation page explains how to implement Amplitude's Web Experiment by adding a script to your website's `<head>` element, providing both synchronous and asynchronous implementation options with anti-flicker snippets, integration methods with third-party CDPs, and specific guidance for content management systems like WordPress and Shopify.

